<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bring-out">bring out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使表现出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He never criticized us, but used praise to <strong>bring out our best</strong>. 
他从不批评我们，而是用称赞使我们表现出最好的一面。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>说出；阐明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most of us can forgive each other when differences are brought out in the open. 
当公开说明分歧时，我们大都能彼此原谅。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can you make a sentence to bring out the meaning of the phrase? 
你能造个句子说明这个短语的意思吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>出版：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They brought out a set of children’s books. 
他们出版了一套儿童读物。</p></div></div>